---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Certificate Policy — VAI"
  description="What a VAI certificate documents, and what it does not confer. Completion criteria, verification, and ethical claims."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Certificate Policy"
    title="What a VAI Certificate Documents — and What It Does Not."
    lede="Plain language on the meaning, scope, and limits of certificates issued by Veterinary Academy International."
  />

  <Section eyebrow="What a VAI certificate documents">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>A VAI certificate documents the completion of a defined postgraduate professional education programme. Each certificate identifies the programme, the issuing academy, the completion criteria met, the version of the programme, and the date of issue.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="What a VAI certificate does not confer" tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Unless explicitly stated and formally recognised by the relevant authority, a VAI certificate <strong class="text-navy-deep font-medium">does not confer specialist status, board certification, or state academic degree equivalence</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Completion criteria">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Certificate eligibility is tied to defined completion components — typically including module assessments, case-based exercises, and a final knowledge check. Components are stated in advance for each programme.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Verification" tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Certificate verification infrastructure is in development. Each certificate will carry a unique identifier verifiable through VAI's verification page.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="CPD/CE recognition">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Where applicable, selected programmes may be submitted to relevant professional bodies for CPD/CE review. <strong class="text-navy-deep font-medium">Any external recognition is communicated only after it has been formally granted.</strong></p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="/cpd-ce-status" class="inline-block text-sm tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-champagne">View CPD/CE Status →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Ethical claims" tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>VAI does not market certificates as equivalents to qualifications they are not. Programme outcomes are described in plain language, and the boundary between professional education and statutory qualification is preserved at all times.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Base>
